OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA largely dry day across the
OL,6,FCentral Belt and south with some
OL,7,Fbright spells. Cloudier across Argyll
OL,8,Fwith a few light showers. Fresh
OL,9,Fsouthwesterly winds at first across
OL,10,Fthe north.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FMainly dry this evening with
OL,13,Fjust a few showers around. Then the
OL,14,Frest of the night will be cloudy with
OL,15,Foutbreaks of rain spreading northeast,
OL,16,Foccasionally heavy.
OL,17,
OL,18,CTuesday:FVariable amounts of cloud and
OL,19,Fsunny spells along with scattered slow
OL,20,Fmoving showers, occasionally heavy in
OL,21,Fthe afternoon. West coast drier later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
