OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FMainly
OL,6,Fdry on Wednesday but some rain likely
OL,7,Fin the evening, mainly in the north. A
OL,8,Ffew early showers on Thursday,
OL,9,Fotherwise dry. Rain spreading east on
OL,10,FFriday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
